				<h1 class="mr-bottom-20">10 Chest And Arm Workouts: The Ultimate Guide For 2025!</h1>
								<div class="single-author mr-bottom-20">
					<div class="name-author">
						<div class="info">
							<div class="author-by" itemscope>
								<time class="updated has-small-font-size" datetime="2024-12-04T01:52:52-08:00"
									itemprop="dateModified">Updated on									December 04, 2024</time>
